# UI Pattern Library - Match Reference Designs

## Design Philosophy
Based on reference apps (Star Communications, FineTune), we follow these patterns:
- **Information-dense but scannable** - Pack features without cluttering
- **Card-based layouts** - Group related content in elevated cards
- **Icon-driven navigation** - Visual icons with labels for clarity
- **Section-based organization** - Clear headers separate content types
- **Bold CTAs** - Primary actions are unmissable

## Dashboard Layout Pattern

### Metric Cards (3-column grid)
```css
.dashboard-metrics {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: var(--spacing-md);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .dashboard-metrics {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

.metric-card {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
}

.metric-card-icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
}

.metric-card-icon--primary {
  background: rgba(226, 195, 61, 0.1); /* Light yellow background */
}

.metric-card-icon--success {
  background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
}

.metric-card-icon--info {
  background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
}

.metric-card-label {
  font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
}

.metric-card-value {
  font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
  font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  line-height: 1;
}

.metric-card-trend {
  font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
  margin-top: var(--spacing-xs);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--spacing-xs);
}

.metric-card-trend--up {
  color: var(--color-success);
}

.metric-card-trend--down {
  color: var(--color-error);
}
```

